The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, helicopter
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
2. the person eating pumpkin is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |
| Food        | pumpkin | blueberry  |
| Birthday       | january | december |
| Transport   | bike    | helicopter |

