2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |
| Cigar    | bluemaster | vegafina  |
| Hobby   | video-games | card-games |
| Pet     | guinea-pig  | lizard     |

